Package org.sensorhub.api.datastore.command

Class CommandFilter

java.lang.Object
org.sensorhub.api.datastore.command.CommandFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Predicate<ICommandData>, IQueryFilter
public class CommandFilter extends Object implements IQueryFilter, Predicate<ICommandData>

Immutable filter object for system commands.
There is an implicit AND between all filter parameters.
